snippet.title: Labyrinth City: Pierre the Maze Detective Trailer - IndieCade 2020
snippet.description:
Wishlist Labyrinth City on Steam: https://bit.ly/Steam_LabCity

Follow Pixmain on Steam: https://bit.ly/PixM_Steam
Follow Pixmain on Twitter: https://twitter.com/pixmain
Follow Darjeeling on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/darjeelingprod

To celebrate the launch of IndieCade 2020, we have made a small trailer for Labyrinth City: Pierre the Maze Detective.

Do not forget to vote for your 3 favorite nominees (we hope Labyrinth City is one of them) during the Anywhere & Everywhere edition here: https://form.jotform.com/202867281885064!



#LabCity #indiegames #indiedev #IndieCade2020
